Sweeping changes loom in the energy docket where a mini -reshuffle  is expected  on a week  detectives are expected to  descend on two state corporations,the Kenya Pipeline company and the National Hospital Insurance Fund – NHIF  for high profile arrests over graft related crimes. The revelations emerged after Director of Public Prosecutions Noordin Haji told the senate justice legal committee that investigations on corruption related crimes at KPC and NHIF are complete.  